<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">⦁40mm Automatic Gun System is the newly designed next generation gun, firing CTA (Cased Telescoped Ammunition) with the rotating chamber. Compared to conventional 40mm guns, the weight and the number of parts have been reduced by more than 50%.
