⦁TGS can rapidly track a target and fire at it, as TADS and Gun are consequently operated according to movements of HMD. Also TGS can operate in several modes such as Stow, Fixed, Flex and MBR.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">Anvil</span></p>
