<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">MULTI-LAYERED AIR DEFENCE SYSTEM</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">The Multi-Layered Air Defence System is an open&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;architecture solution integrating various types of sensors&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;and effectors. Our solution offers unique abilities, state of&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;the art technology and high resilience. The system ensures&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;early warning capability and allows multiple target tracking&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;and interception. C2 core of the system is fully digital and&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;highly automatic, providing functionality in the background&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;with minimal user input. The system is integrated on the&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;TATRA heavy duty chassis ensuring outstanding mobility,&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;performance, and durability.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">LONG-RANGE SURVEILLANCE RADAR SYSTEM</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">The Long-range Surveillance Radar System is a combination&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;of modern S-band 3D highly agile stacked beam AESA&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;primary radar and collocated MSSR-1 Monopulse Secondary&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;Surveillance Radar. The primary radar system shares many&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;components with the RL-series radar systems which have&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;highly modular configuration and low-cost maintenance&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;during its life span. The Long-range Surveillance Radar&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;System have capability to operate as an integrated part&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;of the radar networks and it is ideal for Military Air Traffic&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;Management, Early Warning and Ground Controlled&#38;nbsp;&#60;br&#62;Interception mission.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">CROSS-ROLLER BEARINGS</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Within the cross-roller bearing, cylindrical rollers are arranged with each roller perpendicular to the adjacent roller, in a 90&#38;ordm; V groove, separated from each other by a spacer retainer. This design allows just one bearing to receive loads in all directions including radial, axial and moment loads.&#60;br&#62;Since the cross-roller bearing achieves high rigidity despite the minimum possible dimensions of the inner and outer rings, it is optimal for applications such as joints and swiveling units of industrial robots, swiveling tables of machining centers, rotary units of manipulators, precision rotary tables, cranes, medical&#60;br&#62;equipment, measuring instruments and IC manufacturing machines.&#60;br&#62;&#38;bull; High rotation accuracy&#60;br&#62;&#38;bull; Easy handling&#60;br&#62;&#38;bull; Skewing prevention&#60;br&#62;&#60;br&#62;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">SLEW DRIVES</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">IRAUNDI is a global leader in highly engineered special bearings for many sectors of industry. We have been providing innovative bearing solutions to manufacturers since 1972 and extended our production range with slewing bearings, slew drives, cross-roller bearings &#38;amp; wire race bearings.
IRAUNDI wire bearings are designed and customized for every application. That means that every bearing can be designed according to the customer&#38;rsquo;s structure and specification. We produce up to 3,2 meters slewing bearings, in a different kind of configuration, like internal or external gear, balls or rollers&#38;hellip;
