<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold;">SCORPION&trade; -- Man-Portable ECM</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">SCORPION is Allen-Vanguard&#38;rsquo;s versatile and lightweight man-portable Electronic Countermeasures (ECM) system.&#38;nbsp; It capitalizes on a wealth of operational feedback and a long history of effective ECM to protect personnel from the prevalence of the Radio Controlled Improvised Explosive Device (RCIED) and the growing prominence of Unmanned Aerial Vehicles/Systems (UAV/UAS aka Drones).
The threat against deployed forces has never been greater nor have the demands for effective, robust protection against these RF threats been higher. &#38;nbsp;SCORPION exceeds these needs and delivers a hybrid, full spectrum system with extensive threat band coverage.&#38;nbsp; It is ideally suited for dismounted personnel requiring Force Protection and for EOD Operators seeking a Carry Forward capability. Superior usability, combined with advanced technologies, makes SCORPION a flexible and powerful response to present and future RCIED &#38;amp; Drone threats.</p>
