The 3XXX family offers an internally modular and easily upgradeable architecture with a raft of protection measures.&#38;nbsp; The 3XXX series is robust, simple to operate and maintain, and this combined with its outstanding performance make it ideal for major Non-Governmental Organisations (NGOs) and Other Government Departments (OGDs).</p>
